<!--
    v1.8.8 "Atlas" (Workstream B): Spanish (Español) string catalog.

    Translations reuse the desktop ADR-0023 catalog (crates/rustynes-frontend/
    src/i18n.rs) verbatim where the strings line up — "Configuración" (Settings),
    "Tema" (Theme), "Idioma" (Language), "Restablecer" (Reset), "Cerrar" (Close),
    "Pausa" (Pause), "Sin ROM cargada" — and translate the Android-specific
    surfaces (control bar, RA/netplay/onboarding) accurately to match the same
    register. app_name is intentionally NOT overridden (the brand name is the same
    in every locale, so it falls through to values/).
-->
